WEBVTT

00:11.720 --> 00:15.807
<i>When I first went up this
river, I was sick with love.</i>

00:15.808 --> 00:17.558
<i>The bad kind.</i>

00:17.559 --> 00:20.436
<i>The fist around your heart kind.</i>

00:20.437 --> 00:23.731
<i>I ran far but there was no escaping it.</i>

00:23.732 --> 00:30.029
<i>It followed me upriver all the way.</i>

00:30.030 --> 00:33.115
<i>That was ten long years ago.</i>

00:33.116 --> 00:34.534
<i>A previous episode of a previous</i>

00:34.535 --> 00:39.831
<i>series in a previous life.</i>

00:39.832 --> 00:42.249
<i>Yet here I am again.</i>

00:42.250 --> 00:48.007
<i>Heading up to that same
longhouse in the jungle.</i>

00:53.721 --> 00:59.392
<i>♪ I took a walk through
this beautiful world ♪</i>

00:59.393 --> 01:04.813
<i>♪ Felt the cool rain on my</i> shoulder ♪

01:04.815 --> 01:11.111
<i>♪ Found something good in
this beautiful world ♪</i>

01:11.112 --> 01:17.201
<i>♪ I felt the rain getting colder ♪</i>

01:17.202 --> 01:20.413
<i>♪ Sha la la la la</i>

01:20.414 --> 01:23.624
<i>♪ Sha la la la la la</i>

01:23.625 --> 01:26.502
<i>♪ Sha la la la la</i>

01:26.503 --> 01:29.130
<i>♪ Sha la la la la la la</i>

